text: Geane Rocha (born March 11, 1991) is a Brazilian businesswoman and model based in Valencia, Spain. Rocha was born in Tocantins, Brazil. == Early life and career == Born in Colinas do Tocantins, Brazil, Geane started her professional journey in Goiânia. Initially she started working with buses and moved to real estate at early years of her life. Rocha eventually stepped into modeling in 2016.
